*********************************************************************************************
implicit time out: will wait for objects to be shown
Thread.sleep - waits till the page is stable

- if driver is given 5 seconds implicit timeout - if the locator is found in 2 seconds ->
it will go to next line -> it will not wait for 5 seconds
- it is globally applicable to each and every step

*********************************************************************************************
X path:

//Tagname[@attribute='value']
//Tagname[@attribute='value'][index value]

for CSS selector - by using index value: Tagname[attribute='value']:nth-child[index value]

Xpath: For traversing from parent to child
//parent - tagname/child-tagname[index value]
//tagname[contains(@attribute,'*value')] - this star checks for the starting letters of the value



 css selector : For traversing from parent to child
 parent space child
tagname[attribute*='value'] - this star checks for the starting letters of the value

if we want to identify based on the text :
//tagname[text()='value']
//*[text()='value']


Traversing:
Sibilings- child:
//tagname/tagname/tagname../following-sibiling::tagname[index value]

child - parent:
//tagname/tagname/tagname../parent::tagname

Parent - child relationship:
//xpath //xpath

Absolute Xpath: starts from the root (from the starting of the tag) 
                starts from /
                starts from /html

Relative Xpath: starts from middle
                starts from // 

